Sigma Lithium (SGML) carries a Composite Rating of 63, EPS Rating of 8 and a near-perfect RS Rating of 98.The Canada-based miner aims to promote EV growth by producing low cost and environmentally sustainable lithium products.

Tesla has reportedly made a bid for lithium stock Sigma Lithium, according to Bloomberg. Sigma is poised to start commercial lithium production at its Brazil site in April.

The Brazilian mine will produce spodumene concentrate, which is a source of lithium hydroxide for EV batteries.